{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十五回千变万化，火魔神以埋藏于山坪四周的火药胁迫天下群豪臣服，揭露他收买异邦武士安装火药、利用公孙红清除无用棋子的连环毒计。他宣布一切所为皆是为了方宝玉，命宝玉当众陈冤。宝玉声泪俱下揭露自己被迫屈从的缘由，铁娃痛哭追随。火魔神自承设计陷害宝玉，令江湖中人误解于他。宝玉进而指认石不为才是杀害几位叔父的真凶，石不为以七大门派门户之仇煽动群豪反击，双方各执一词，群豪盲从摇摆。火魔神突揭石不为自己早已收买，莫不屈震惊崩溃，石不为却以诡辩自辩。群豪再度被煽动冲锋之际，七八位神秘长衫客以内力连环推手分开人群登上擂台，齐声命令七大门派弟子不得出手，当众揭下面具，身份即将揭晓。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "火药……火药！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火药在哪里？……还有没有……是谁放的？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "火药在哪里，只有我知道。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "在哪里？……在哪里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我费了一年之力，将蜀中唐家、山西柳家、云南白家、中原霹雳堂、江南火鸟庄这些武林中暗器火药名家他们家里积存的火药全都运到这里，其力量之大小，各位可想而知。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "这些火药此刻便埋在这山坪四周，旁边都有人看守，只要我号令一发，那些人在一瞬间便可将火药点燃。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "你如此做法，为的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_mu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一木大师",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "对了，你究竟要怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我要你们一个个站在这里闭住口，未得我同意，谁也不许动弹，不许说话，否则我便将这片山坪整个化为灰烬。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "但那些异邦武士，岂非……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "那些异邦武士也都早已被我收买。他们七年前来到中土，带来了大批珍宝，本为了有求于紫衣侯，哪知紫衣侯民族气节凛然，竟不为之所动，而他们带来的珍宝，却都落人了别人手中。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "落人了谁的手中，你么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "他们任务既未达成，珍宝又已失去，自不敢再回到他们自己的国度而流落中土。他们虽都是无恶不作的恶徒，怎奈形貌太过引人注目，武功又不甚高，是以劫掠所获，并不甚丰，不但生活甚是落魄潦倒，而且还要四处流窜、逃避，是我稍加示意之后，他们便都乖乖地投入了我门下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "不错，他们武功若是高强，又怎会被我一网打尽？但他们既是如此不济，你又为何要将他们收录门下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "只因这些人武功虽不济，但他们的国度中却将火药使用得甚是普遍，他们对火药的知识自然也颇丰富，对于安装引线、埋藏火药以及引发爆炸之事，这些人可说无一不是绝顶好手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "speaker_name": "公孙红",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "原来你是要利用他们此点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "不错，这些人正都是我利用的工具。火药安装妥当，他们的利用价值也就完了，我正不知该如何将他们除去，那时你恰巧来了，我便故意在他们藏身之处说些要加害此间群豪的毒计，诱你闻声而出。我正要假你的手将这些已成无用的废物杀死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_hong",
      "text": "正是如此，你才会找他们，否则这些异邦武士聚在一起，说的自是异邦之言，他们就算在你身旁商量毒计害人，你也万万不会听得懂的。如此简单的道理，你难道一直都想不起么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "你还要怎样？说吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我如此做法，本来自是要将你们这些自命侠义的人物全都置之死地，但后来，我的主意却改变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "变为怎样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "只因我后来想到，若是在暗中将你等全都炸死，我纵能称霸江湖，但你们全都死了，既瞧不见我的威风，也不会对我生出畏惧之心，我岂非等于辛苦写了一篇文章却无人欣赏？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_mu_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "一木大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，只有死人才是真正的英雄铁汉，对任何人、任何事都再也不会惧怕。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "是以我便想，与其将你等全都炸死，倒不如让你们活着瞧瞧我的威风，以生死之事来威胁你等听命于我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "这些人虽或也有些威武不能屈的硬汉，但也少不得有些人会乖乖听我话的，而一个活人为我做的事就比千百个死人多得多，何况……那是万万不止一个人的，是么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "但此刻我又改变了主意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "又变为怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "如今我已不能再要你等为我做事。我如此做法，已全都是为了一个人，只因他一个人能为我做的事，委实比你们这些人加在一起都多，此刻他既已答应肯为我做事，他无论要我对你们怎样，我都不会迟疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "丁老夫人",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "他便是方宝玉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你有什么话要对他们说，此刻只管说吧，我相信再也不会有人敢打断你的话，再无人敢伤你一根毫发。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "说话呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "不错，我要说话，我有许多话要说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "此刻站在我面前的，有待我恩重如山的师叔，有与我亲如骨血的兄弟，有视我如子如侄的前辈，也有慷慨与我论交的朋友……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我瞧着这些与我情深义重的叔伯兄弟被一个我所痛恨的人如此胁迫，我心中实在如万箭钻心一般，但……但我却只能在一旁瞧着，我……我……我委实不得不如此做法，只因……只因我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "只因我若不如此，便不能说话，只因世上只有他……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "只有他能让我说话，只因你们都冤枉了我，误会了我，我若不说话，这冤屈便永远无法得伸，我死……死也不瞑目。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "大哥，告诉铁娃，是谁冤枉了大哥，是什么事冤枉了大哥，大哥，你……你快告诉我，铁娃跟他拼命。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "大弟，你……你真……真好。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "你要问我怎会受这些冤屈，不如问他。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "这红毛猴子，是你怎样冤枉了我大哥？快说！快说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "不错，那时我为了要方宝玉听命于我，便要断绝他在江湖上的生路。我为了要断绝他的生路，便只有使江湖中人俱都误解于他。只要他肯为我做事，他是恨我是骂我，我全不放在心上。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我令人假冒欧阳天矫的妻子，以药酒将他灌醉，令他第二日再也不能与欧阳天矫动手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "我又令人伪装受伤，要他出手解救，使他功力受损，又无法与'天刀'梅谦动手，好叫别人因此轻贱于他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_qian",
      "speaker_name": "梅谦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来如此。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "不仅如此，我还令人改扮成方宝玉的模样，到梅谦处投下书信，声明从此退出江湖，好叫别人更要认为他是怯战而逃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "那封书信果然是假的……果然是假的……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "这畜牲如此害你大哥，你就在这里呆看着他不动么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "你这红兔子，如此害我大哥，我跟你拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "大哥为何叫我站住？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "你也想害我么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "小……小弟哪敢害大哥，这……这……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "你不让他说完话，我的冤屈便永远无法洗清，这不是在害我又是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "你如此轻举妄动，他若不顾一切，将火药引发，那后果又会怎样？你不但害了我，也害了别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "铁娃本不敢出手的，但……但石四叔却……却要我出手，铁娃想连石四叔都这样说话，那想必是没有关系的了，哪知……哪知却有这么大的关系！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "老四，忍耐些。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "text": "铁娃，你可知石四叔为何要如此说话么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_niu_tie_wa",
      "speaker_name": "铁娃",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只因无论你做了什么事，咱们都还是对你好的，你四叔他听得别人如此害你，自然难免激愤失常。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "大叔对小侄之心意，小侄全都知道，大叔的宽宏仁慈之心，更令小侄感动，但……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "但大叔此番却错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我什么错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "石四叔如此做法，只因他一心要害我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "畜牲！放屁……我为何要害你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "只因你生怕火魔神说出一些话来，你要将我与火魔神全都杀死灭口，是以你便要如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "不错，我是要将你置之死地……只因你无论曾经受过多么大的冤屈，但你毒手将公孙二哥、金不畏、魏不贪、西门老六、杨不怒……这些待你恩重如山的人杀死，却是千真万确之事。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "少林、武当、峨嵋、崆峒、淮南、点苍……七大门派的弟子们，你们的掌门师兄，就是被这畜牲害了，这畜牲就是你们门户的仇人，'门户之仇，人人得而诛之'，这戒条你们难道忘了么？你们若还容这畜牲站在那里，便是违背了门规，便是门户的叛徒。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "各位切莫听他之言，害死我那几位叔父的真凶，其实另有其人，决不是我方宝玉。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不是你，是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "那真凶虽然始终藏头露尾，但说话的声音我却听到过，那时我已觉他说话的声音极是熟悉，只是一时想不起他是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "他语声你既十分熟悉，又怎会听他不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "只因此人平日极少说话，纵然说话，也不过只是三五个字而已，是以要掩饰他的语声，自是容易得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "谁？此人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "就是他——石不为。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "宝儿，你疯了么？怎可胡乱含血喷人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "此乃千真万确之事，宝儿哪敢在天下英雄之前胡言乱语？宝儿实已想了又想，才敢说出这番话来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "老四，你……你怎不出言辩驳？难道你无话可说么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "如此胡言乱语，全无丝毫证据，直如疯狗咬人一样，在下若是出言辩驳，岂非也和疯狗一般见识了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "宝儿，你如此说话，可有证据？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "证据便在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "不错，我便是证据，只因这些事都是我要石不为做的，石不为他委实也早已被我收买。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "真的？……这会是真的？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "此事说出之后，七大门派若要为弟子复仇，我也难逃其责，这责任是何等重大，我怎会说假？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "石不为，你还待狡辩？你还有何话说？还是快快承认了吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你……你还有何可笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "这些话本只能骗骗三尺童子，不想大哥你竟也相信了，却叫小弟如何不笑？哈哈！如何不笑？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "事已至此，我……我已不得不信。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "这些日子来，我始终追随大哥左右，纵有离别，也不过一时半刻，难道我竟会在这一时半刻中被人收买么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "text": "何况，我石不为纵要被人收买，也要货卖识家，怎会卖给此等无信无义的卑鄙无耻之徒？难道我会那般愚蠢，连此人以后是否会出卖我都瞧不出，难道我竟会将自己的性命、名声视如儿戏？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "莫不屈",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "这……唉！老四你日后究竟要为善为恶，我虽瞧不出，但……但我却深信你绝非如此愚蠢的人。若说此等人物，也可以些许金银珠宝将你收买，我……我委实越想越难以相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "此事实是显而易见，各位难道还瞧不出么？他两人早已串通好了，要来陷害于我，各位怎能上他们的当？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "不错，这话有理，咱们可千万不能上他的当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "这样的人，若还要他活在世上，实是武林之羞……七大门派的弟子们，你们能容得这叛徒么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "容不得……容不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "火药！火药！你……你们难道不要命了么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "text": "你若是要用火药，还会等到此刻？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_mo_shen",
      "speaker_name": "火魔神",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你，你难道不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "不错，火药是有的，但火药若是爆炸，连你也要死在这里，你敢么？……朋友们，还不冲上去？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冲呀……冲上去！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "speaker_name": "长衫客",
      "listener": "char_qun_hao",
      "text": "七大门派下的弟子，谁也不准出手。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "text": "你是什么东西，有何资格命令七大门派弟子？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "speaker_name": "长衫客",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你可知道我等是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "石不为",
      "listener": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "text": "石某正要瞧瞧你是谁！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "speaker_name": "长衫客",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "你要瞧瞧我是谁么？好……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_shan_ke",
      "speaker_name": "长衫客",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_wei",
      "text": "且瞧我是谁。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    }
  ],
